07:15.297 --> 07:16.554
That's fascinating.

07:17.999 --> 07:19.792
I've been doing it
for about eight years now.

07:19.802 --> 07:21.863
I, uh... I mean, more seriously now

07:21.874 --> 07:23.540
for... I, well...
I've never been onstage.

07:23.551 --> 07:26.299
I would be so honored
if I could show you

07:26.309 --> 07:28.035
