No!

09:22.366 --> 09:25.860
No, no!

09:25.870 --> 09:28.240
No!

09:29.442 --> 09:31.435
Beatrice, are you in here?

09:34.447 --> 09:35.839
Beatrice!

09:35.849 --> 09:37.045
Aw, how'd you know it was me?

09:37.056 --> 09:39.776
Well, I'm looking right at you. How
long have you been waiting there?

09:39.787 --> 09:40.807
