09:55.738 --> 09:57.363
Why not let nature be your sleeves?

09:57.373 --> 09:59.965
And most importantly,
you need to look impressed

09:59.975 --> 10:01.399
when I conjure...

10:01.409 --> 10:03.404
the mystical arts!

10:03.415 --> 10:04.769
Collapsible bouquet.

10:04.779 --> 10:06.575
Yes.

10:06.586 --> 10:09.080
Okay, but let me try something else.

10:09.091 --> 10:10.143
