10:29.172 --> 10:31.398
I mean...

10:37.914 --> 10:40.475
This... this mayor.

10:40.485 --> 10:43.345
He was a fine, upstanding gentleman.

10:43.355 --> 10:45.212
- He was a girl.
- Of course, a girl.

10:45.222 --> 10:47.483
That's... what I was saying.
An upstanding woman.

10:47.493 --> 10:49.451
- She was a dog.
- Yes, a dog.

10:49.461 --> 10:52.687
A female... dog.

10:52.697 --> 10:54.724
Big, fluffy, huge... Chihuahua.

10:54.734 --> 10:56.425
Little tiny Chihuahua.

10:56.435 --> 10:57.926
