12:46.604 --> 12:48.745
- Oh.
- And it's caramel, not butterscotch.

12:48.755 --> 12:50.715
We've got three packages.

12:50.725 --> 12:53.485
Number one: the New Faces, where I
bring you up for one quick trick.

12:53.485 --> 12:55.620
