the Champagne Excelsior.

13:00.702 --> 13:03.395
You get your own show, private venue,

13:03.405 --> 13:06.800
fully nude, in front of
an audience of strangers.

13:06.810 --> 13:08.735
As far as what goes down
in that theatre...

13:08.745 --> 13:11.238
well, that's dealer's choice.

13:11.248 --> 13:12.706
Let's go with number two.

13:12.716 --> 13:13.740
Well, suit yourself.

13:14.884 --> 13:16.857
- Oh, excuse me. Magic man?
- Yes?

13:16.868 --> 13:18.845
Do you have the time?

13:18.855 --> 13:20.882
Where's your watch?

13:20.892 --> 13:23.384
- Very nice trick.
- ♪ Ta-da ♪

13:23.394 --> 13:25.052
