14:13.948 --> 14:17.908
This is a regulation straightjacket.

14:17.918 --> 14:18.943
Tie it tight.

14:18.953 --> 14:20.244
I'm bored.

14:20.254 --> 14:23.916
Mm. Does anyone like watching magic?

14:25.495 --> 14:27.119
- Done!
- And now...

14:27.129 --> 14:28.486
the escape!

14:32.969 --> 14:35.387
You have to pop
your shoulder out of the socket.

14:35.398 --> 14:36.696
You're not the magician.

14:36.706 --> 14:40.033
I am. Women are not magic. Except
that one thing where you can make

14:40.043 --> 14:42.134
a human form inside of you.
That's really magic.

14:42.144 --> 14:44.837
That Elaine is beautiful.

14:46.484 --> 14:48.942
Would anybody like to see a trick?

14:48.952 --> 14:50.611
