- Me, me!

14:50.621 --> 14:52.413
Frederick, pick a number.

14:52.423 --> 14:55.450
Ah... ooh, math was not my strong suit.

14:55.460 --> 14:57.817
Uh... all right.

14:57.827 --> 15:00.688
Is your number... seven?

15:00.698 --> 15:01.922
