15:23.890 --> 15:26.750
Oh, I get it. It's Blanche.

15:30.597 --> 15:32.656
I just know the ghost is Mayor Cutie.

15:32.666 --> 15:34.959
Oh. I wonder if having been bones

15:34.969 --> 15:37.294
will change her love for them
in any way.

15:37.304 --> 15:39.464
Thank you for joining me

15:39.474 --> 15:42.466
at the table of the gods.

15:46.581 --> 15:49.241
Can anybody else see her?

15:58.894 --> 16:02.022
Shh, shh, shh. I hear something faint...

16:02.032 --> 16:06.259
an ushering in
of the all-seeing spirits.

16:06.269 --> 16:09.662
Now... anyone you'd like to see?

16:09.672 --> 16:12.432
I want to see Mother.

16:12.442 --> 16:14.201
She's right there.

16:14.211 --> 16:16.071
Mother, it's me, Frederick.

16:16.081 --> 16:18.072
- Can you hear me?
- Of course...

16:20.251 --> 16:22.210
Oh, wow. He is good.

16:25.724 --> 16:27.124
Whoa!

16:32.831 --> 16:34.557
Garfield!

16:34.567 --> 16:36.459
A supernatural presence
is close at hand.

16:36.469 --> 16:38.893
I can feel it. Set the bait, boys,

16:38.903 --> 16:40.363
set the bait.

16:40.373 --> 16:42.265
Here is paté for the ghost-dog,

16:42.275 --> 16:45.134
here is a wire hanger
for the ghost-baby.

16:45.144 --> 16:47.937
Trio of home-baked macarons for...

16:47.947 --> 16:49.572
Sticky Jonathan.

16:49.582 --> 16:53.510
But Mr. Peepers, that's my best friend.

16:53.520 --> 16:55.113
Other people will die.

16:55.123 --> 16:58.214
You'll make friends with their ghosts.

16:58.224 --> 16:59.717
Mr. Peepers,

16:59.727 --> 17:01.885
how do you know so much about ghosts?

17:04.900 --> 17:06.258
Garfield...

17:09.637 --> 17:12.797
I've never told anybody
this story before,

17:12.807 --> 17:18.002
but my great-great-great-grandpappy...

17:18.012 --> 17:20.038
was a ghost.

17:20.048 --> 17:22.941
Yes, Garfield, I have ghost blood

17:22.951 --> 17:27.446
coursing through me.
It is my family's eternal shame.

17:27.457 --> 17:30.018
Is that why they call you Spiritwalker?

17:30.028 --> 17:32.987
What? Oh, no, no. Don't be ridiculous.
They call me Spiritwalker

17:32.997 --> 17:34.822
because I walk
with such great enthusiasm.

17:34.832 --> 17:36.123
Observe.

17:38.169 --> 17:39.861
Oh!

17:39.871 --> 17:41.761
Oh, Mr. Peepers!

17:41.771 --> 17:45.834
Mister... oh! Look out!

17:45.844 --> 17:49.003
Mr. Peepers, look at you go!

17:49.013 --> 17:52.105
Oh, my goodness.

17:58.057 --> 17:59.615
Oh, please be Mayor Cutie.

17:59.625 --> 18:02.117
Please be Mayor Cutie!

18:08.067 --> 18:12.496
Here comes... a being of smoky mystery.

18:12.506 --> 18:15.499
- It's Cutie!
- The Major Cutie!

18:15.509 --> 18:18.000
- No... Mayor Cutie.
- Mayor Cutie!

18:18.010 --> 18:20.069
Come!

18:20.079 --> 18:21.838
No, no! No!

18:21.848 --> 18:23.141
If you touch that glass,

18:23.151 --> 18:25.409
you will pierce the veil between worlds.

18:25.419 --> 18:27.278
We will all surely perish.

18:27.288 --> 18:29.417
I don't care about perishing!
That's my dog in there.

18:29.428 --> 18:31.048
No!

18:31.058 --> 18:33.685
Ooh, I almost got my wrist free.

18:35.897 --> 18:37.422
Cutie!

18:37.432 --> 18:41.359
You came back from doggy heaven.

18:41.369 --> 18:43.562
It's Cutie!

18:43.572 --> 18:45.008
Wait a second.

18:47.743 --> 18:49.970
This spot is painted on!

18:49.980 --> 18:51.537
Imposter!

18:51.547 --> 18:53.239
You're a flimflam man!

18:53.249 --> 18:54.874
Well, conjure complete.

18:54.884 --> 18:57.009
I bid you adieu!

18:57.019 --> 18:58.645
God damn smoke pellets.

19:05.596 --> 19:06.954
Albert-kazam!

19:08.965 --> 19:11.826
Take him away, officers.

19:11.836 --> 19:14.062
Well, there was no spirit after all.

19:15.641 --> 19:17.031
No spirit?

19:17.041 --> 19:20.301
The trap has caught the specter!
Everybody follow.

19:21.913 --> 19:24.207
Ghost...

19:24.217 --> 19:26.276
The ghost trap has been sprung!

19:26.286 --> 19:29.287
The phantasm is among us. Stay back!

19:29.288 --> 19:32.481
Ghost Mother, you haunt me still!

19:32.491 --> 19:34.816
Oh, Frederick, I'm not a ghost.

19:34.826 --> 19:37.787
You just saw me downstairs.
Unholy wraith!

19:40.901 --> 19:43.326
Holy Christ!

19:43.336 --> 19:44.729
Mayor Cutie.

19:44.739 --> 19:49.601
He-Devil speaks the name
of the white man's lord!

19:54.348 --> 19:55.973
Hi, Daddy.

19:55.983 --> 19:57.976
I thought you were a real ghost.

19:57.986 --> 19:59.655
Hello, family.

20:05.961 --> 20:08.854
I'm sorry I thought
you were a ghost, Mother.

20:08.864 --> 20:10.557
Father was the ghost all along!

20:10.567 --> 20:12.391
He's no ghost.

20:12.401 --> 20:14.527
He's been living in the walls

20:14.537 --> 20:16.529
like some sort of rat.

20:16.539 --> 20:19.799
I built these walls.
I can live in them if I want to.

20:19.809 --> 20:21.934
You'll do no such thing.

20:21.944 --> 20:26.205
This is my house now.
You live here no more.

20:26.215 --> 20:28.976
Shrew!

20:28.986 --> 20:32.912
- What a rip-off.
- Bye, Daddy.

20:32.922 --> 20:34.692
So, am I the ghost?

20:36.445 --> 20:38.653
What should we call you?
Bark when you like one.

20:38.663 --> 20:40.389
Councilwoman Snuggles.

20:40.399 --> 20:42.191
Burgermeister Schlussi?

20:42.201 --> 20:44.160
Ooh, Guadalupe Festiva.

20:44.170 --> 20:46.428
Oh, you're right.

20:46.438 --> 20:48.596
I'll just pretend you're Mayor Cutie.

20:50.174 --> 20:52.066
I'm so sorry I killed you.

20:54.513 --> 20:56.672
I hope I don't have to do it again.

